text: St James's Church Hall, Fortis Green Road end. St James's Church Hall is a church hall in Fortis Green Road, Muswell Hill, London, and a grade II listed building with Historic England. It was built in 1925 to a design by George Grey Wornum. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Grade II listed buildings in the London Borough of Haringey Category:Muswell Hill
